Hannah Spearritt https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hannah_Spearritt 0 Hannah Louise Spearritt (born 1 April 1981) is an English actress and former singer. She is an original member of the pop group S Club 7 from 1999 until they split in 2003. In November 2014, the group announced plans for an arena reunion tour, Bring It All Back 2015, which toured the UK in May 2015. Spearritt is also known for playing the role of Abby Maitland in the drama Primeval. Hannah_Louise_Spearritt ( born 1_April_1981 ) is an_English_actress and former_singer .
